  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A Phase I,open label study to assess the safety and tolerability of ZD6474 in combination
      with 5-Fluorouracil, Leucovorin and Oxaliplatin (mFOLFOX6) as first and second line therapy
      in patients with advanced colorectal adenocarcinoma.
    </textblock>
